Monitor memory usage:

- [ ] No memory leaks
- [ ] Smooth scrolling with many beasts
- [ ] No crashes on low-memory devices

### Battery Usage

Check battery impact:

- [ ] Reasonable battery consumption
- [ ] No excessive CPU usage
- [ ] WebSocket connections don't drain battery

